那又是大约20分钟。

345
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:36,680
After that, I have my daily makeup routine.
之后，我还有每天的化妆流程。

346
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:37,680
True.
确实。

347
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:41,520
I hardly ever see you without your hair done and your makeup on, even when you show up
我几乎从没见过你头发没打理、没化妆的样子，即使你

348
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:43,280
