interesting to see if you have any other type of routine.
很有趣，看看你们有没有其他类型的流程。

368
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:05,920
I know some people wake up in the morning, and the first thing they do, they always walk
我知道有些人早上醒来，第一件事总是遛狗，

