比如。

370
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,280
Oh, that's very nice.
哦，那很好。

371
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:12,800
Other people are very hungry, so they almost always eat right when they wake up.
其他人很饿，所以他们几乎总是在醒来时就吃东西。

372
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:14,920
