我在刷牙前吃东西。

373
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:15,920
Smart, actually.
其实挺聪明的。

374
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:19,200
Yeah, alright, so we want to hear from you guys.
是啊，好了，所以我们想听听你们的意见。

375
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:20,200
Come to EnglishPod.com.
来 EnglishPod.com。

376
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:21,200
